_eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZUjUz4H5coBHcVgc_bE3KdzEcMIQ8czf6oUf-lf_Z0__3UolODH-_KnRdpLK7V7f_apczMbFNE12OURQL2SGicyPlDvabC0K-dgDBaO31vxB4mV6qWYq0YXhKN7CDhlmJfogYMX1rL3IPBLbcnXAt9lAnwpv5dP_V25qVBm1B5H4dUr_sUB1bKa_KGteKJh-3Q&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#Bailarin</a></span>, un bello caballo saino que al verla le relinchaba, sus ojos eran enormes y brillaban, parecian dos soles, que iluminaban hacia donde miraba.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: inherit;\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Cuando lo volvio a ver, no pod&iacute;a creer en el estado en el que estaba <span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x6umtig x1b1mbwd xaqea5y xav7gou x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv x1qq9wsj xo1l8bm\" style=\"cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; list-style: none; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; touch-action: manipulation; display: inline; font-family: inherit; border: 0px initial initial;\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/bailarin?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZUjUz4H5coBHcVgc_bE3KdzEcMIQ8czf6oUf-lf_Z0__3UolODH-_KnRdpLK7V7f_apczMbFNE12OURQL2SGicyPlDvabC0K-dgDBaO31vxB4mV6qWYq0YXhKN7CDhlmJfogYMX1rL3IPBLbcnXAt9lAnwpv5dP_V25qVBm1B5H4dUr_sUB1bKa_KGteKJh-3Q&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#Bailarin</a></span>, se le veian las costillas, le dolian las manos al caminar y su mirada era de pura tristeza y dolor, su miraba estaba apagada.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r x1vvkbs xtlvy1s x126k92a\" style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px; overflow-wrap: break-word; white-space: pre-wrap; font-family: inherit;\">\r\n<div dir=\"auto\" style=\"font-family: inherit;\">Hoy m&aacute;s que nunca <span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x6umtig x1b1mbwd xaqea5y xav7gou x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv x1qq9wsj xo1l8bm\" style=\"cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; list-style: none; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; touch-action: manipulation; display: inline; font-family: inherit; border: 0px initial initial;\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/melina?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZUjUz4H5coBHcVgc_bE3KdzEcMIQ8czf6oUf-lf_Z0__3UolODH-_KnRdpLK7V7f_apczMbFNE12OURQL2SGicyPlDvabC0K-dgDBaO31vxB4mV6qWYq0YXhKN7CDhlmJfogYMX1rL3IPBLbcnXAt9lAnwpv5dP_V25qVBm1B5H4dUr_sUB1bKa_KGteKJh-3Q&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#Melina</a></span> y <span style=\"font-family: inherit;\"><a class=\"x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x6umtig x1b1mbwd xaqea5y xav7gou x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 xe8uvvx xdj266r x11i5rnm xat24cr x1mh8g0r xexx8yu x4uap5 x18d9i69 xkhd6sd x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz xt0b8zv x1qq9wsj xo1l8bm\" style=\"cursor: pointer; text-decoration-line: none; outline: none; list-style: none; margin: 0px; text-align: inherit; padding: 0px; box-sizing: border-box; background-color: transparent; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; touch-action: manipulation; display: inline; font-family: inherit; border: 0px initial initial;\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"link\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hashtag/bailarin?__eep__=6&amp;__cft__[0]=AZUjUz4H5coBHcVgc_bE3KdzEcMIQ8czf6oUf-lf_Z0__3UolODH-_KnRdpLK7V7f_apczMbFNE12OURQL2SGicyPlDvabC0K-dgDBaO31vxB4mV6qWYq0YXhKN7CDhlmJfogYMX1rL3IPBLbcnXAt9lAnwpv5dP_V25qVBm1B5H4dUr_sUB1bKa_KGteKJh-3Q&amp;__tn__=*NK-R\">#Bailarin</a></span> tienen una conexi&oacute;n &uacute;nica que dif&iacute;cilmente podr&aacute; romperse, el destino los u